       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. DC-SLASH-COMMAND-REGISTER.

       DATA DIVISION.
       LINKAGE SECTION.
       01 DC-SLASH-COMMAND-JSON PIC X(8192).
       COPY "discord-result.cpy".

       PROCEDURE DIVISION USING DC-SLASH-COMMAND-JSON DC-RESULT.
       MAIN.
           MOVE DC-STATUS-ERROR TO DC-STATUS-CODE
           MOVE "DC_ERR_HTTP_NOT_IMPLEMENTED" TO DC-ERROR-CODE
           MOVE "Slash command registration needs HTTP transport."
               TO DC-ERROR-MESSAGE
           GOBACK.
       END PROGRAM DC-SLASH-COMMAND-REGISTER.
